---
// Historia de ESYMBEL Cafetería
---

<!-- Historia Section -->
<section id="historia" class="relative overflow-hidden py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-28 min-h-screen">
  
  <!-- Decoraciones de fondo -->
  <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-10 left-10 opacity-10">
    <svg width="120" height="180" viewBox="0 0 120 180" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <ellipse cx="20" cy="30" rx="15" ry="20" fill="#d97706" opacity="0.3"/>
      <ellipse cx="50" cy="80" rx="15" ry="20" fill="#d97706" opacity="0.3"/>
      <ellipse cx="80" cy="130" rx="15" ry="20" fill="#d97706" opacity="0.3"/>
      <ellipse cx="35" cy="155" rx="15" ry="20" fill="#d97706" opacity="0.3"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="hidden md:block absolute bottom-20 right-20 opacity-10">
    <svg width="200" height="200" viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M100 20 Q120 60 100 100 Q80 140 100 180 M80 50 Q100 70 80 90 M120 110 Q100 130 120 150" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.3"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Título con línea decorativa -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16 lg:mb-20"  data-aos="zoom-out-right" data-aos-duration="1000">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-light text-stone-700 mb-6 md:mb-8 leading-relaxed px-4">
          De nuestro corazón<br/>a tu taza
        </h2>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <div class="h-px bg-amber-600 w-20 md:w-32"></div>
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></div>
          <div class="h-px bg-amber-600 w-20 md:w-32"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contenido principal -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        
        <!-- Lado izquierdo: Lista de valores -->
        <div class="space-y-8 md:space-y-12">
          
          <!-- SOMOS LOCALES -->
          <div class="flex gap-4 md:gap-6 items-start group">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-14 h-14 md:w-20 md:h-20 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
                <rect x="20" y="40" width="60" height="40" stroke-width="2" rx="2"/>
                <path d="M30 40 L30 30 Q50 20 70 30 L70 40" stroke-width="2"/>
                <circle cx="50" cy="55" r="8" stroke-width="2"/>
                <line x1="40" y1="70" x2="60" y2="70" stroke-width="2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1000">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600 mb-2 md:mb-3">
                SOMOS LOCALES
              </h3>
              <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed">
                Nacimos en esta comunidad y servimos con orgullo a nuestros vecinos, creando un espacio donde todos se sientan como en casa.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- SOMOS ARTESANALES -->
          <div class="flex gap-4 md:gap-6 items-start group">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-14 h-14 md:w-20 md:h-20 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
                <path d="M30 70 L40 40 L60 40 L70 70 Z" stroke-width="2"/>
                <path d="M35 70 L35 85 L65 85 L65 70" stroke-width="2"/>
                <circle cx="50" cy="30" r="8" stroke-width="2"/>
                <path d="M42 30 Q50 35 58 30" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
                <line x1="42" y1="60" x2="58" y2="60" stroke-width="2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1000">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600 mb-2 md:mb-3">
                SOMOS ARTESANALES
              </h3>
              <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed">
                Cada bebida es preparada a mano con dedicación. No usamos automáticos porque creemos en el valor del trabajo artesanal.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- SOMOS PASIÓN -->
          <div class="flex gap-4 md:gap-6 items-start group">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-14 h-14 md:w-20 md:h-20 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
                <path d="M50 75 Q35 60 35 45 Q35 30 45 25 Q50 22 50 30 Q50 22 55 25 Q65 30 65 45 Q65 60 50 75 Z" stroke-width="2"/>
                <path d="M45 40 Q50 45 55 40" stroke-width="2"/>
                <circle cx="42" cy="38" r="2" fill="currentColor"/>
                <circle cx="58" cy="38" r="2" fill="currentColor"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1000">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600 mb-2 md:mb-3">
                SOMOS PASIÓN
              </h3>
              <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed">
                Amamos lo que hacemos y se nota en cada taza. Seleccionamos los mejores granos y preparamos todo con amor y paciencia.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Lado derecho: Imagen circular -->
        <div class="relative flex justify-center lg:justify-end mt-8 lg:mt-0">
          <!-- Decoración de fondo -->
          <div class="hidden lg:block absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-amber-600/5 rounded-full"></div>
          
          <!-- Imagen principal -->
          <div class="relative z-10" data-aos="flip-left" data-aos-duration="1000">
            <div class="relative w-64 h-64 sm:w-80 sm:h-80 md:w-96 md:h-96 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
              <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1495474472287-4d71bcdd2085?w=800&q=80" 
                alt="Barista preparando café en ESYMBEL"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-900/30 to-transparent"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Decoración floral -->
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute bottom-0 right-0 opacity-20">
            <svg width="150" height="150" viewBox="0 0 150 150" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M75 75 Q90 65 100 75 Q110 85 100 95 Q90 105 75 95" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="2"/>
              <path d="M75 75 Q85 60 95 50 Q105 40 115 50" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="2"/>
              <path d="M75 75 Q65 90 55 100 Q45 110 35 100" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<script src="./historia.js"></script>